[154.251304, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[?25l\u001b[H\u001b[38;5;246m← \u001b[48;5;153m\u001b[38;5;16m ☐ Client shape \u001b[39m\u001b[49m ☐ Profiles  ☐ Four-layer  ✔ Submit  →\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;231m\u001b[1mWhen the DevPulse app is closed on a client machine, should ingestion sources \u001b[22m\u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;231m\u001b[1m(watched folders/repos) keep flowing to clyffy?\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;153m❯\u001b[3G\u001b[38;5;246m1.\u001b[6G\u001b[38;5;153mApp-only for v1, agent later (Recommended)\r\u001b[1B\u001b[39m \u001b[3G   \u001b[38;5;246mV1 ships only the DevPulse app — ingestion runs while it's open. The \u001b[76G\u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B   \u001b[38;5;246moptional headless agent (same device identity, attaches like a dispatcher) \r\u001b[1B\u001b[39m     \u001b[38;5;246mis schema-ready\u001b[22Gvia branch 2's \u001b[38Gttachm\u001b[46Gt roles and\u001b[58Gships as a later\r\u001b[5C\u001b[1Bceremo\u001b[13Gy, \u001b[17Gike estate-move/QR.\u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;246m2.\u001b[6G\u001b[39mHeadless\u001b[15Gagent\u001b[21Gfrom\u001b[26Gday\u001b[30Gone\r\u001b[5C\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;246mEvery DevPulse install includes an optional background service that keeps \r\u001b[1B\u001b[39m \u001b[3G   \u001b[38;5;246mwatching source\u001b[23Gwith the\u001b[32Gapp closed. More moving parts (service install \r\u001b[1B\u001b[39m     \u001b[38;5;246mper OS =\u001b[15Gadmin prompts, contradicting bra\u001b[48Gch 1's no-admin-\u001b[65Grompts win), but\r\u001b[5C\u001b[1Bmaximum\u001b[14Gingestion continuity.\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B3.\u001b[6G\u001b[39mApp-only,\u001b[16Gpermanently\r\u001b[1B     \u001b[38;5;246mThe client is only ever the app; if it's closed nothing ingests. Simplest \r\u001b[1B\u001b[39m     \u001b[38;5;246mpossible story, but forecloses continuous-capture on client machines.\r\u001b[1B\u001b[39m  \u001b[38;5;246m4. Type something.\r\u001b[1B────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\r\u001b[1B\u001b[39m  5. Chat about this\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;246mEnter to select · Tab/Arrow keys to navigate · Esc to canc\u001b[60Gl\u001b[39m\u001b[K\u001b[23;1H\u001b[6;1H\u001b[?2026l"]
