[183.806557, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[H\u001b[38;5;246m────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\r\u001b[1B\u001b[39m←\u001b[4G☒\u001b[6GClient\u001b[13Gshape\u001b[19G\u001b[48;5;153m\u001b[38;5;16m ☐ Profiles \u001b[32G\u001b[39m\u001b[49m☐\u001b[34GFour-layer\u001b[46G✔\u001b[48GSubmit\u001b[56G→\r\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;231m\u001b[1mClyffy-side: t\u001b[16Gansport + s\u001b[28Gssion machinery always-on in EVERY resource profile \r\u001b[1B(Lite-12GB up to 3-Spark ring), with profiles scaling only the model \r\u001b[1Broster/funnel depth?\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[5C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;153m❯\u001b[3G\u001b[38;5;246m1.\u001b[6G\u001b[38;5;153mYes — contract is profile-invariant (Recommended)\u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[5C\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;246mEvery profile serves the identical /v1 + QUIC contract; ResourceProfile at \r\u001b[5C\u001b[1Bboot picks model\u001b[23G/funnel depth. A client never knows or cares which profile\r\u001b[1B\u001b[39m \u001b[3G  \u001b[6G\u001b[38;5;246mit hit. Matches the resource-aware law and the no-topology-hardcoding \r\u001b[5C\u001b[1Bcor\u001b[10Gection.\u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;246m2.\u001b[6G\u001b[39mNo — small profiles get a reduced contract\u001b[K\r\u001b[5C\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;246mLite profiles drop the fast p\u001b[36Gth (HTTP-only)\u001b[51Gto save resources. Saves \u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[5C\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;246mlittle in practice a\u001b[27Gd forks the client contract into two behaviors.\r\u001b[4C\u001b[1B Type something.\u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;246m────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[39m4.\u001b[6GChat about this\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;246mEnter to select · Tab/Arrow keys to navigate · Esc to cancel\u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[2B\u001b[K\u001b[23;1H\u001b[8;1H\u001b[?2026l"]
