[190.70405, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[H←  ☒ Client shape  ☒ Profiles \u001b[48;5;153m\u001b[38;5;16m ☐ Four-layer \u001b[39m\u001b[49m ✔ Submit  →\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;231m\u001b[1mFour-layer placement: transport/session seam = SURFACE concern (Brain API \r\u001b[1Bsur\u001b[5Gace), with de\u001b[19Gtructive-op gating exp\u001b[42Gessed at the capability-pack layer?\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;153m❯\u001b[39m \u001b[38;5;246m1.\u001b[39m \u001b[38;5;153mSurface owns transport; packs own risk-gates (Recommended)\r\u001b[5C\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;246mDevPulse = variant; Brain API = surface owning QUIC upgrade + attach/outbox\r\u001b[1B\u001b[39m \u001b[3G  \u001b[6G\u001b[38;5;246mplumbing; capability-packs declaratively gate read/write/destructive on \r\u001b[5C\u001b[1Bwork-items (branch 2's gate lands here);\u001b[47GMCP-leaves untouched. Transport \u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[5C\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;246mstays \u001b[13Gnvisibl\u001b[21G to packs.\u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;246m2.\u001b[6G\u001b[39mTransport as its own capability-pack\u001b[K\r\u001b[5C\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;246mM\u001b[8Gdel \u001b[13Ghe fast path itself as a pack so it's declaratively gated/versioned \r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[39m  \u001b[6G\u001b[38;5;246mlike other capabilities. Misfits: packs describe WHAT clyffy can do, not \r\u001b[5C\u001b[1BHOW bytes move; risk-gating\u001b[34Ga wire makes every capability transiti\u001b[74Gly \r\u001b[5C\u001b[1Bdepend\u001b[13Go\u001b[16Git.\u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[4C\u001b[1B Defer four-layer\u001b[23Gmapping\u001b[31Gto\u001b[34Gthe\u001b[38Gfold\r\u001b[1B     \u001b[38;5;246mDecide only client/profile shape now; let the fold place the seam when the \r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[39m  \u001b[6G\u001b[38;5;246mwhole plan is on the table.\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B4. Type something.\r\u001b[1B────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[39m5.\u001b[6GChat\u001b[11Gabout\u001b[17Gthis\r\u001b[2B\u001b[38;5;246mEnter to select · Tab/Arrow keys to navigate · Esc to cancel\u001b[39m\u001b[23;1H\u001b[6;1H\u001b[?2026l"]
