[200.719427, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[H\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;246m────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\r\u001b[1B\u001b[39m←  ☒ Client shape  ☒ Profiles  ☒ Four-layer \u001b[48;5;153m\u001b[38;5;16m ✔ Submit \u001b[49m\u001b[38;5;246m →\u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;231m\u001b[1mReview your answers\r\u001b[1B\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[1C\u001b[1B●\u001b[4GWhen the DevPulse app is closed on a client machine, should ingestion sources\r\u001b[3C\u001b[1B(watched folders/repos) keep flowing to clyffy?\u001b[K\r\u001b[3C\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;114m→ Headless agent from day one\u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[1C\u001b[1B●\u001b[4GClyffy-side: transport + session\u001b[37Gmachinery\u001b[47Galways-on\u001b[57Gin\u001b[60GEVERY\u001b[66Gresource\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B profile (Lite-12GB\u001b[23Gup to 3-Spark ring),\u001b[44Gwith\u001b[49Gprofiles\u001b[58Gscaling\u001b[66Gonly\u001b[71Gthe\u001b[75Gmodel\r\u001b[3C\u001b[1Broster/funnel depth?\u001b[K\r\u001b[3C\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;114m→ Yes — contract is profile-invariant (Recommended)\u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[1C\u001b[1B●\u001b[4GFour-layer placement: transport/session seam = SURFACE concern (Brain API\r\u001b[3C\u001b[1Bsurface), with destructive-op\u001b[34Ggating\u001b[41Gexpressed\u001b[51Gat\u001b[54Gthe\u001b[58Gcapability-pack\u001b[74Glayer?\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B \u001b[38;5;114m→ Surface owns transport; packs own risk-gates (Recommended)\r\u001b[5C\u001b[1B\u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;246mReady t\u001b[9G submit\u001b[17Gyour answers?\u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;153m❯\u001b[39m \u001b[38;5;246m1. \u001b[38;5;153mSubmit answers\u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;246m2. \u001b[7G\u001b[39mancel\u001b[K\r\u001b[2B\u001b[K\u001b[23;1H\u001b[20;1H\u001b[?2026l"]
